C Number of events
EVCT-NEVT 20000
C
C Particle Code (14 = nmu)
EVCT-IDPT 14
C Just leave these in for now; it defines direction etc of neutrino
EVCT-MPOS 2
EVCT-RAD  100.
EVCT-MDIR 1
EVCT-DIR 0. 0. 1.
EVCT-MPV 3
C Name of the root file containing flux
EVCT-FILENM  'MCC9_FluxHist_volTPCActive.root'
C Name of the flux histogram inside the root file
EVCT-HISTNM  'hEnumu_cv'
C Is the histogram in MeV or GeV; if in MeV set to 1
EVCT-INMEV 0
C
C **** TARGET INFORMATION ****
C 22 Bound neutrons
NEUT-NUMBNDN 22
C 18 bound protons
NEUT-NUMBNDP 18
C No free protons
NEUT-NUMFREP 0
C 18+22=40
NEUT-NUMATOM 40

C Generate in all modes
NEUT-MODE 0

NEUT-CRSPATH='../neut/src/crsdat'
NEUT-RAND 1
C Want NEUT to be quiet
NEUT-QUIET 2

C Generate with Nieves 2p2h
NEUT-MDL2P2H 1

C Generate with Nieves 1p1h with LFG, revert to RFG with BBBA05 when not possible
NEUT-MDLQE 2002

